x10.matrix.block

Class DenseBlock

  • x10.matrix.block.MatrixBlock
    • x10.matrix.block.DenseBlock

  • public class DenseBlock
extends MatrixBlock
    Dense block is used to build dense block matrix (at single place) or distributed dense matrix at all places.
